history.proof: intros m k H. induction m. - simpl. reflexivity. - simpl. inversion H as [H1 H2]. apply IHm in H1. rewrite H1. hauto lq: on depth: 3. - simpl. inversion H as [H1 H2]. hauto use: not_exd_nil unfold: prec_L, nil inv: sumbool.

exceptions.exn: Wrong bullet -: Current bullet - is not finished.

original: intros m k H. induction m. - simpl. reflexivity. - simpl. inversion H as [H1 H2]. apply IHm in H1. rewrite H1. reflexivity. - simpl. inversion H as [H1 H2]. apply IHm in H1. destruct H2 as [H2 _]. rewrite H1. reflexivity.
